Top-rated clothing sizes refer to the sizes with the highest ranking based on customer feedback, where ranking is determined by the accuracy of the size fit and the customer's rating, with the most accurate and highest-rated feedback ranked first; 
The top 3 feedback for each clothing size are considered; 
The converted size in France is the size equivalent in the French standard.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT size_name
FROM clothing_sizes
WHERE INSTR(fitting_guide, 'true') > 0;

SELECT size_name 
FROM clothing_sizes 
WHERE size_id = 1;

SELECT size_name, usa_size
FROM clothing_sizes
WHERE usa_size = (
    SELECT MIN(usa_size) 
    FROM clothing_sizes
);
